						               													<description>It's about God and the world and a dream of congregations. Each player directs one of eight congregations that thrives, grows and prospers: the Catholic cathedral, a national Protestant church, a classic free church, a start-up, the small-town congregation, the city church, the event church or a international congregation.&amp;#10;You win by doubling the worship attendance to 150 visitors, by raising all your qualities to the value 7 or by a third way - because it is about the triune God - but this is a secret and can only be experienced in the game.&amp;#10;To do so, the players are playing cards and roll dice.&amp;#10;The game is played in rounds of three phases:&amp;#10;Phase 1: Reflection - Draw up to five cards.&amp;#10;Phase 2: Use - Play up to three cards and throw dices for most of it.&amp;#10;Phase 3: Traditions - Applying of exisiting traditions and establishing new traditions, which give you &amp;quot;bonus&amp;quot; till end of the game(traditions cannot be abolished that easy so bonus may become bothersome later).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
